name: Tamu Shampoo
description: Tamu Shampoo is free of sulfates and made with herbs that gently cleanse and stimulate the scalp.  Indulge in the sweet aromas of vanilla & ylang ylang with each wash.

name: Tamu Conditioner
description: Tamu Conditioner is enrinched with wheat germ oil, which is a great source of essential fatty acids that are vital for healthy hair growth.  The light, creamy texture penetrates hair follicles and has great slip, which makes detangling an ease.  Tamu Contitioner can also be used as a leave-in conditioner.  Great for "twist-outs" & "braid-outs"

name: Hair Puddn'
description: Hair Puddn' is a buttery hair cream jam-packed with nutritious herbs and natural oils that fortify hair follicles and encourages growth.  Excellent moisturizer for hair and scalp.

name: BrownSugaBabe Body Cream
description: Moisture-rich mango butter blended with lush natural oils that encourage soft, radiant skin.  Laced with essences of creamy coconut.

name: Sweet Thang Body Cream
description: Moisture-rich mango butter blended with lush natural oils that encourage soft, radiant skin.  Laced with a floral, sweet fragrance...reminds us of cherry blossoms.

name: Sole Therapy Foot Cream
description: is a superb and rich blend of mango and shea butters...the ideal moisturizer for extremely dry feet.  Laced with essential oils of eucalyptus and peppermint to relax aching feet and tea tree oil to eliminate odor causing bacteria.  Sole Therapy will give you summer feet...all year long!
